# Running the Tests{\n}
{\n}
## *NIX/Mac OS X{\n}
{\n}
From the root of the project, simply run{\n}
{\n}
`gradle --info test`{\n}
{\n}
if you do not have gradle installed, try:{\n}
{\n}
`gradlew --info test`{\n}
{\n}

## Windows{\n}
{\n}
From the root of the project, simply run{\n}
{\n}
`gradle --info test`{\n}
{\n}
if you do not have gradle installed, try:{\n}
{\n}
`./gradlew.bat --info test`{\n}
{\n}

{\n}
The `--info` switch will also output logging for the tests{\n}
{\n}
